逼巴士西鐵，<br />\n<br />\n次次都好似玩欖球咁格壓沖入去，無計，鬼叫你窮咩。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好啦放工增修完捱完成日難得見到西鐵有吉位又唔敢坐又怕比人放上網公審後生仔唔捱得。<br />\n<br />\n晚晚12點幾先番到屋企，<br />\n<br />\n沖個涼連電視都冇得睇就要訓，<br />\n<br />\n如果唔係又唔夠精彩做野比腦細屌。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n第二朝又6點起身準備番工。<br />\n<br />\n搵日唔好彩遲左起身坐的士又冇左成日人工，<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唉，做香港人wo...<br />\n<br />\n講民主，講理想，講做香港人有幾咁自豪，原來，真係得個講字..."},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T07:13:16.000Z","msg":"個撚個香港人都係咁㗎喇，你唔撚想做香港人咪死撚咗佢囉，你唔九care 理想同民主大撚把人care"},{"pid":"7f22ecc29b86759d7b53cfc7c4d338af33156df7","tid":650742,"uid":9683,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T09:04:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8663775659080284f0c44412d6c9d24c7fb3d4f0","tid":650742,"uid":89981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T09:17:16.000Z","msg":"香港幾時有好過"},{"pid":"9637e4e2e8b1ec3d2f60c8dbeee72a2dfda96c7d","tid":650742,"uid":1886,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"de1fdf677ff1a39f3b15962b822362ee25e02b59","tid":650742,"uid":86841,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"a847c53054be09cd2692a3c36ed5571ffe0b7e0d","tid":650742,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7714d7e5302820010cac6b45115b32a911ab2152","tid":650742,"uid":86841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T05:50:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T06:19:44.000Z","msg":"撐本土得罪你？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T06:47:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T09:34:57.000Z","msg":"政策以本土優先、捍衛本土文化 = 盲反？<br />\n<br />\n發達民主國家同城市有邊個唔係以本土人為優先？"},{"pid":"caefd9fdc6252aebd7703fc09be7bfdc4d462a82","tid":650742,"uid":117786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T09:37:11.000Z","msg":"建議樓主幫自己拎個英國人頭銜<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2afe977715780bcc3c68e040ccac1af1762f4e62","tid":650742,"uid":9683,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"c